      • add

        public boolean add(Overlay overlay,
                   boolean overwrite)
        Add an overlay. If overwrite is false, only add it when there is no other overlay intersecting with it. If overwrite is true, remove overlays intersecting with the new overlay and then add it.
        Parameters:
        overlay - the overlay which shall be added
        overwrite - true, if intersecting overlays shall be overwritten
        Returns:
        true, if added, false if not added
